location.fullValue: San Saba Plan, Silos at La Sienna

data.description: This exceptional two-story home, boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms, along with a 2-car garage. Open floor plan, spacious design & lofty ceilings, this home offers a truly inviting ambiance. The main bedroom is conveniently located on the ground floor, complete with a full bathroom featuring a double vanity, a jetted tub, a standalone shower & a generously-sized walk-in closet. Includes a well-equipped gym on the lower level. Upstairs, are 3 additional bedrooms, a Jack and Jill bathroom, & an irresistible theater room perfect for entertainment. Situated within the beautiful planned & gated community of La Sienna, this home is ideally located near major expressways, top-rated schools, as well as a variety of shopping and dining options. As an added bonus, this property comes with a stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, storage shed, & an outdoor playground set. Sellers offer up to $10,000 for buyer closing costs for offers at $429,000.
